project.name: Pinnacle
project.description: Pinnacle is a 36-hour hackathon designed to offer a higher tier of competition above the collegiate hackathon scene. We partner with the top collegiate hackathons in the world and invite their winners to an ultimate, 36-hour event, coined as "the Olympics of Hackathons." Our event entirely funded by third party sponsors and powered by our volunteer team members. Pinnacle is backed by Hack+, a 501c3 nonprofit organization that helps students launch businesses, nonprofits and events.
